# Build context is the submission root. Keep it lean: ship only the Rust
# workspace sources, migrations, and the vendored Resources/.

# Rust build artifacts (huge; rebuilt inside the image)
**/target/

# VCS
.git/
**/.gitignore

# Node / Playwright e2e (not needed in the runtime image)
**/node_modules/
e2e/

# Editor / OS cruft
.vscode/
.idea/
**/*.swp
**/.DS_Store

# Local env and secrets — NEVER bake into an image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Docs that don't affect the build
**/*.md
